com.software.reuze

Class m_Fraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.software.reuze.m_Fraction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<m_Fraction>

    public class m_Fraction
extends Number
implements Comparable<m_Fraction>, Serializable
    A class representing fractions as pairs of ints. Fractions are always maintained in reduced form. Denominator is always positive
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
